<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/52227615-the-buddhist-on-death-row"><img alt="The Buddhist on Death Row: How One Man Found Light in the Darkest Place" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1582467231l/52227615._SX98_.jpg" />
